{"tid":531234,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"倒8支清潔劑落溫泉變「泡泡浴」　日本兩少年被捕","createTime":"2018-01-16T14:44:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-19T14:30:40.000Z","uid":33213,"like":216,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"60bb256ddc35fe15c03e225ca41aff125d26e4a7","tid":531234,"uid":33213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T14:44:07.000Z","msg":"日本和歌山縣警方今日（1月15日）拘捕兩名少年，罪名係妨礙營業，因為兩人惡作劇搞到當地溫泉「一鑊泡」。 <br />\n<br />\n據《產經新聞》報道，事發於昨年8月，日本和歌山縣新宮市熊野川町的溫泉設施「熊野川溫泉Satsuki」，按摩浴池被人倒入至少8支洗頭水及沐浴露變成「泡泡浴」，浴池及地板都充斥番梘泡。事件令溫泉需要臨時關閉兩小時進行清潔，按摩浴池亦要停用清潔直至同月19日。 <br />\n<br />\n警方其後從閉路電視鎖定疑犯汽車，本月11日在三重縣松阪市先拘捕其中一人，今日再拘捕另一人。兩人已承認在事發當日，與朋友到當地享用溫泉時作案。<br />\n<br />\n涉事設施在2011年一度被豪雨沖毁，其後改建並重新營業，被當地居民視為復興的象徵，豈料會遭人大整蠱。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DTli1kZX0AAaq5s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDTli1kZX0AAaq5s.jpg&h=3b75bf2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DTli1gBX0AEodUM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDTli1gBX0AEodUM.jpg&h=678aec91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DTli1i4W4AAcmhf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDTli1i4W4AAcmhf.jpg&h=6916598b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DTli1kYWAAA-u1T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDTli1kYWAAA-u1T.jpg&h=4ab38b62&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"72fe6b0c0e1b60de9c96341ebcf5b55c6d5fe3cc","tid":531234,"uid":22913,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T14:50:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7d9c73ee018fe7a3c486c322a4aca967d962fd9","tid":531234,"uid":52215,"like":184,"dislike":1,"score":183,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T14:52:18.000Z","msg":"咁撚衰格"},{"pid":"e09ca4e476d15af4b42bd